Package edu.odu.cs.cs350.dupedetector

Class PropertiesFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.odu.cs.cs350.dupedetector.PropertiesFile
  • public class PropertiesFile
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds and process's data that are used for the programs properties. These are either provided by an .ini file on the CLI or resorts to defaults if not provided. They follow a format of propertyName = propertyValue There exist three primary properties in: CppExtensions MinSequenceLength MaxSubstitutions
